<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb924b403-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea" identifier="/us/usc/t5/s9009"><num value="9009">§ 9009.</num><heading> Cost accounting standards</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The cost accounting standards issued pursuant to section 1502(a) and (b) of title 41 shall not apply with respect to a long-term care insurance contract under this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idb924b404-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/106/265/tI/s1002/a">Pub. L. 106–265, title I, § 1002(a)</ref>, <date date="2000-09-19">Sept. 19, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/769">114 Stat. 769</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/111/350/s5/a/19">Pub. L. 111–350, § 5(a)(19)</ref>, <date date="2011-01-04">Jan. 4, 2011</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/124/3842">124 Stat. 3842</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idb924b405-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idb924b406-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idb924b407-5e84-11f1-a692-ec26948f6fea"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2011—<ref href="/us/pl/111/350">Pub. L. 111–350</ref> substituted “section 1502(a) and (b) of title 41” for “section 26(f) of the Office of Federal Procurement Policy Act (<ref href="/us/usc/t41/s422/f">41 U.S.C. 422(f)</ref>)”.</p>
</note>
